    <title>Solving a Linear Equation in One Variable</title>
    <p><em>Solving a Linear Equation in One Variable</em> demonstrates the process for solving for a single 
        variable x in an equation that has no exponents. You may be asked to distribute and combine like 
        terms prior to isolating the variable.</p>
        
